channel.title: Comments on: Flight of the Conchords full-length due in April

item.title: By: Jack
item.dc:creator: Jack
item.description: Great news!! Love the Concords. <a href="http://www.8hands.com/musicblog/The_8hands_Mega_Team_Puts_An_End_To_2007_Part_5" rel="nofollow">this blog</a> chose them as best EP of 2007! I personally think it should be Black kids, but the concords are just as awesome.
